  "events": [
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00001",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 1,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "仉氏上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00002",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "引子",
      "speakers": [
        "仉氏"
      ],
      "text": "玉洁冰清，抚孤儿，昼夜辛勤。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00003",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "仉氏"
      ],
      "text": "岁寒松柏抱坚贞，茅舍竹篱伴此身。留待孤葵承雨露，不使冰操负初心。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00004",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "仉氏"
      ],
      "text": "老身仉氏。先夫孟公宜，不幸中年亡故。留下一子名唤孟轲，年方十岁。只为家业萧条，纺织度日。居住在临街小巷，与那些屠户为邻。怎奈我那孟轲孩儿，不知务正，也学那屠牛宰马，教我放心不下。今日趁我纺织余暇，不免唤他出来教训一番。正是：",
      "text_length": 112
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00005",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "仉氏"
      ],
      "text": "欲培佳子弟，须种好心田。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00006",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "仉氏"
      ],
      "text": "恨苍天太无情月圆难久，怅离群悲寂处蹙损眉头。勤纺织改变了纤纤素手，为孤儿荒学业日夜担忧。访邻居常使我劳心费口，看起来这长街不可停留。",
      "text_length": 66
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00007",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "仉氏"
      ],
      "text": "待我将姣儿唤出，教训一番。孟轲哪里？",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00008",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内白",
      "speakers": [
        "孟轲"
      ],
      "text": "来了！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00009",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "孟轲上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00010",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "孟轲"
      ],
      "text": "过屠门只见些剔骨剜肉,倒使我豪侠气陡上心头。莫道我年幼小狠心辣手，要宰那普天下无道的诸侯。",
      "text_length": 45
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00011",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孟轲"
      ],
      "text": "母亲在上，孩儿拜揖！",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00012",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "仉氏"
      ],
      "text": "罢了。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00013",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孟轲"
      ],
      "text": "将孩儿唤将出来，有何训教？",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00014",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "仉氏"
      ],
      "text": "你每日在街巷与那些邻舍儿童，玩耍些什么？",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00015",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孟轲"
      ],
      "text": "孩儿在外，不喜与那些儿童玩耍；最喜的是那些杀猪宰羊的营生。",
      "text_length": 29
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00016",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "仉氏"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀儿呀，你这小小的年纪，不学长进，怎么学起那杀猪宰羊的营生来了？",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00017",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孟轲"
      ],
      "text": "母亲，岂不闻古人有云：“乱臣贼子，人人得而诛之”。孩儿学那宰割猪羊，就如同杀那乱臣贼子。想那些乱臣贼子，被孩儿杀尽，岂不痛哉！岂不快哉！",
      "text_length": 68
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00018",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "仉氏"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀儿呀，你不要满口乱道。听为娘教导于你。",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00019",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "仉氏"
      ],
      "text": "叫孟轲我的儿听娘指授，待为娘对吾儿细说从头：儿的父遭不幸中年夭寿，抛下了母子们苦度春秋；为娘我勤纺织把光阴来度，皆因是儿年小、家业空、盼只盼、数年之后、教子成名、好对我那孟氏坟丘。我的儿呀！",
      "text_length": 95
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00020",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "孟轲"
      ],
      "text": "母亲教训儿谨受，走近膝前说从头：儿虽然年幼小心思浅陋，怎学那市井之徒无赖之尤！",
      "text_length": 39
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00021",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "仉氏"
      ],
      "text": "有一辈圣贤空前绝后，待为娘学说古圣根由：仲尼少年陈俎豆，到后来率门徒宣道德列国周游；设教杏坛制礼定乐，讲易删诗述作春秋。儿若是效法那先师指授，立志勤学定把名留。",
      "text_length": 80
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00022",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "仉氏"
      ],
      "text": "儿啊，你看那亘古以来，哪一个圣贤不从那少年经过。但是父母的教训，只许你读书养气，岂容学那市井之徒！况为娘盼子成人，教儿的心切；惟恐儿任气纵性，攻乎异端，不得正道，失没根基。为娘所教儿的言语，须要紧记心头。",
      "text_length": 102
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00023",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孟轲"
      ],
      "text": "孩儿谨记在心。以往过错，望母亲恕过！",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00024",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "仉氏"
      ],
      "text": "为娘倒有个主意，你我母子何不迁移在城外乡村，离开这市井的繁华，以便儿明心养性，你看如何？",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00025",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孟轲"
      ],
      "text": "孩儿遵命。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00026",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "仉氏"
      ],
      "text": "好个孝顺的儿呀！",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00027",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "仉氏"
      ],
      "text": "为孤儿移性情循循善诱，远屠沽近庄农为善的关头。但愿你持正气与圣贤厮守，教为娘宽怀抱散虑消愁。",
      "text_length": 46
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00028",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "仉氏、孟轲同下。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00029",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内白",
      "speakers": [
        "常守文"
      ],
      "text": "啊哈！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00030",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "常守文上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00031",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "数板",
      "speakers": [
        "常守文"
      ],
      "text": "命苦身贫，命苦身贫，世人拿我不当人。只因我，衣不遮体，常常赤半身。饭不能饱，每日只能吃半顿。为度残生给人照应坟。可怜我，饥寒困苦常与鬼为邻，常与鬼为邻！",
      "text_length": 76
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00032",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "常守文"
      ],
      "text": "我常守文。就是这邹国人氏。祖居在这个村儿，给公卿大人们照管坟墓。因此人都叫我常守坟。只因我国和鲁国搭界，可恨那鲁国倚强欺弱，时常侵犯我国，因此我国不断的向百姓们征兵征赋，闹得全国“老者转于沟壑，壮者散而之四方”了。就拿我们村儿说吧，人口萧条，住户减少。我要不是给公卿大夫们照管坟墓，早就被征去当兵啦。这且不言，我们村儿里，新由城里搬来个孟老太太，带着个十来岁的小孩子，孤儿寡母，很是清苦。最奇怪的是那个小孩子，每天愁眉泪眼，咳声叹气，自言自语，疯疯癫癫。那么点儿的小孩子，真仿佛个五十多岁的人那么多愁多虑的样子。还不如我这穷小子没心没肺，得过且过，随遇而安哪！",
      "text_length": 280
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00033",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "常守文"
      ],
      "text": "近日里村落中炊烟减少，人口稀住户少景况萧条。我虽然贫苦身褴褛衣帽，觉天宽与地阔并不心焦。看在这坟茔中不觉狂笑，",
      "text_length": 55
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00034",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "常守文笑。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00035",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "常守文"
      ],
      "text": "富与贵贫与贱一个土包。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00036",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内白",
      "speakers": [
        "孟轲"
      ],
      "text": "走哇！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00037",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "常守文"
      ],
      "text": "远远望见那个小孩来啦，待我听他说些什么！",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00038",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "孟轲上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00039",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "孟轲"
      ],
      "text": "叹光阴如过客百年非久，朝复夕夕还朝日月轮流。青山绿水还依旧，一抔土也不知几历春秋。凄风苦雨残碑朽，野花闲花满月愁。问天不语空搔首，触目伤心不自由。悲从中来泪湿衣袖，泪湿衣袖、我那亡父啊！抛下了母子们寡侣失俦。",
      "text_length": 104
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00040",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "常守文"
      ],
      "text": "我说这小孩，你有什么症候吧？",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00041",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孟轲"
      ],
      "text": "原来是坟少爷！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00042",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "常守文"
      ],
      "text": "好说您哪。我问问你，你天天这么愁眉苦脸的，为了什么呀？",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00043",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孟轲"
      ],
      "text": "老丈，你看蓬蒿遍野，古墓成堆。想人生在世，不过百年，无非如此。岂不令人伤心惨目，教我岂得不愁？",
      "text_length": 47
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00044",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "常守文"
      ],
      "text": "我问问你，您今年高寿啦？",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00045",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孟轲"
      ],
      "text": "年方十岁。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00046",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "常守文"
      ],
      "text": "您才十岁，就打这个算盘，多早晚您才愁的完哪！",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00047",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孟轲"
      ],
      "text": "休得取笑。看前面青山隐隐，绿水迢迢，何不同去一观？",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00048",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "常守文"
      ],
      "text": "我还有事，不能奉陪。公子请便吧！",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00049",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孟轲"
      ],
      "text": "如此说，少陪了。正是：",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00050",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "孟轲"
      ],
      "text": "贤愚千载知谁是，早晚蓬蒿共一丘。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00051",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孟轲"
      ],
      "text": "请。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00052",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "孟轲下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00053",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "常守文"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀，只顾跟他瞎聊，我的晚饭还没准备出来哪。我得准备晚饭去！",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00054",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "常守文下。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00055",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "仉氏、孟轲同上。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00056",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "仉氏"
      ],
      "text": "荒郊外渺茫茫山明水秀，村落里人烟少风景清幽。为孤儿避繁华迁移未久，怎奈他双眉锁整日忧愁。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00057",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "仉氏"
      ],
      "text": "儿呀，你我母子迁移在这村庄以内，看那些风清月白，水秀山明，正好畅意开怀，涵养那中和之气。怎么你，不是学那些埋葬的仪节，就是学那吊祭的悲哀？我看你小小的年纪，是这样抑郁不舒，岂不堕落了英雄志气！难道说，这村庄居住，就不能悦性怡情了么？",
      "text_length": 116
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00058",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孟轲"
      ],
      "text": "母亲所说言语，孩儿领会。岂不知这村居野处，悦性怡情；怎奈一见荒丘垒垒，古墓成堆，不由得痛彻心肺，想起去世的爹爹来了！",
      "text_length": 58
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00059",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "仉氏"
      ],
      "text": "儿待怎讲？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00060",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孟轲"
      ],
      "text": "想起去世的爹爹来了！",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00061",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "仉氏、孟轲同哭。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00062",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "仉氏"
      ],
      "text": "听我儿言悲惨壮心灰透，",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00063",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "三叫头",
      "speakers": [
        "仉氏"
      ],
      "text": "亡父，孟轲，儿呀！",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00064",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "仉氏"
      ],
      "text": "不由我肝肠断痛泪交流。娘本意避繁华为儿迁就，又谁知反惹起儿思父的念头。倘若是儿有个天长地久，教为娘怎对那孟氏坟丘！",
      "text_length": 57
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00065",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "仉氏"
      ],
      "text": "儿呀，如此说来，在这村中居住，倒是为娘的不是了？",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03020001_e00066",
      "play_id": "03020001",
      "scene_id": "03020001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
